            <title>[LU-2348] e2image produce invalid image for a large xattr patch.</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-2348</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;after some investment we found a e2image don&apos;t collect valid image for a large ea files because data blocks for that inode isn&apos;t added to copy.&lt;br/&gt;
also we don&apos;t have a way to obtain a external journal from system, except a copy whole device, which may be too big.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
